&lt;p data-start=&quot;135&quot; data-end=&quot;429&quot;&gt;At Alpine Eagle, we’re building the future of counter-drone defence. We’re a fast-growing, international deep-tech company working at the intersection of aerospace engineering, defence systems, and machine learning. Our goal: create the world’s first swarm-based, airborne counter-drone system.&lt;/p&gt;
