&lt;p&gt;This role demands a &lt;strong&gt;strong personality&lt;/strong&gt;, a &lt;strong&gt;resilient mindset&lt;/strong&gt;, and the ability to negotiate under pressure while keeping strategic objectives in focus. If you thrive in high-stakes environments and can &lt;strong&gt;balance structure with agility&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll feel at home here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead end-to-end project management across cross-functional teams (engineering, procurement, testing, and customer success).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage multiple defence-related programs, ensuring compliance with contractual, technical, and security requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary point of contact for military and government clients&amp;nbsp; as well as our product development teams - maintaining trust, accountability, and transparent communication.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee project timelines, milestones, and budgets; anticipate risks and apply corrective actions early.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive negotiations with suppliers, subcontractors, and partners to secure optimal terms and maintain project momentum.&lt;/li&gt;
